<title>bḥr mḥbẗ ạlfạdy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1-
 bḥr mḥbẗ ạlfạdy lạ yḥd mtsʿ ạlạ̉rjạʾ
 fy ṭwlh wʿmqh srmdy wmạ
 lh ạstqṣạʾ
 ạlqrạr- qd fạq ḥbh qd zạd fḍlh
 ạ̹dẖ jʿlny hyklạaⁿ lrwḥh
 gẖdwt wạrtẖạaⁿ llh fy ạlmsyḥ wtrnmt sẖftạy bạltsbyḥ
 (kl mạly fy ạlḥyạẗ
 kl ʿmry llmmạt)2
 llḥbyb llḥbyb mn fdạny bạlṣlyb
 2-
 fy mwth tlạqy̱ ʿly̱ ạlṣlyb ạlbr wạlslạm
 bnṣrẗ ạlqyạmẗ sẖms ạ̉ḍạỷt flạsẖt ạlẓlạm
 3-
 blṭfẗ ạlʿjyb sby̱ fw̉ạdy ạ̉zạl ḥmạ̉ty
 ạ̉ḍḥy̱ kdẖạ mjny trs kẖlạṣy ynbwʿ nṣrty</lyrics>
</song>